rows.label: qev012203_MSG0002
rows.name:
I was tightening the last screw here just as I heard
the gunfire die off.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012203_MSG0003
rows.name:
This is the first time I've really taken part in a team
operation. Pretty neat![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012203_MSG0004
rows.name:
I may have more of a knack for this than
I first thought...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012203_MSG0005
rows.name:
Anyhoo, the enemy turret's down and my Skell's back
up, so it's time to get back to adventuring![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012203_MSG0006
rows.name:
Next up is... Hmm, maybe I'll head north
and check out Cauldros.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012203_MSG0007
rows.name: Meanwhile, I owe you big time! Er, again...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012203_MSG0008
rows.name:
Role models like you who look after others
get nothing but respect in my book.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012203_MSG0009
rows.name: Welp, time waits for no woman. I'm off![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012203_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Mia about your reward for helping her.

rows.label: qev012203_MSG0012
rows.name:
Hope we can team up again the next time
our paths cross![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012203_MSG0013
rows.name:
Who knows, maybe next time you'll see me
in combat! Exciiiting![ST:wait ]
